definitions.text:
@để mắt
- Keep a keen eye on
=Để mắt đến việc học của con cái+To Keep a keen eye on one's children's studies

@để không
- Leave empty, leave unused
=Ngôi nhà để không+A house left unused

@để tang
- Wear mourning for, be in mourning for
=Để tang bố+To be in mourning for one's father

@để lộ
- Let out
=Để lộ bí mật+To let out a secret

@để ý
* verb
- to pay attention; to regard; to take notice of

@để mặt
- Let be, leave alone
=Để mặc nó+Leave him alone

@để của
- Leave (money or property) to somebody.
-(cũ) Bury one's wealth

@để kháng
- Resist
=ổ để kháng+Pocket of resistance

@để mà
- In order to, in order that, so that, so as to
=Ăn để mà sống+To eat in order to go on living, to eat in order to live

@đểnh đoảng
- Lukewarm, tepid
=Tình cảm đểnh đoảng+Lukewarm feelings

@để cho
- In order that, in order to, so that, so as to
=Bón phân nhiều để cho lúa tốt+To manure abundantly so that the rice plants grow well
